Class MultipleExceptionResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.jsonrpc4j.MultipleExceptionResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExceptionResolver

    public class MultipleExceptionResolver
extends java.lang.Object
implements ExceptionResolver
    ExceptionResolver that supports the use of multiple ExceptionResolver used one after another until one is able to resolve the Exception.
